  <notepads>
    <notepad>
      <note>Workshop 6: Multi-Stage LLM Pipeline

This transformation chains 5 sequential LLM calls:
1. Classification → Identify document type
2. Priority Scoring → Rate urgency 1-10
3. Info Extraction → Extract type-specific details
4. Action Generation → Create action items
5. Department Routing → Assign to team

Each stage uses outputs from previous stages!</note>
